metadata.name: January Picto-grid
metadata.description:
This is the full spread of January doodles

PASK Doodles is a project centered around daily doodles completed in 2023. This collection is intended to be a companion piece to the journey in character exploration and story telling that PASK Doodles represents. Those who collect, save, and burn will be rewarded. This will be a living, growing, evolving art project.
